OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FBreezy in the north with sunny
OL,6,Fspells and showers for Northern
OL,7,FIreland, Scotland and northern
OL,8,FEngland, but clearing later. Southern
OL,9,Fareas stay dry and bright, though low
OL,10,Fcloud may affect the far southwest.
OL,11,FCooler further north, warm fin the
OL,12,Fsouth.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FShowers in the north
OL,15,Fgradually fade as winds ease
OL,16,Fovernight. Elsewhere, skies clear,
OL,17,Fespecially in the south, with some
OL,18,Fpatchy fog possible later across the
OL,19,Ffar southwest by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
