OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FEarly mist or fog in the
OL,6,Fsouthwest, otherwise mostly dry with
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Light showers in
OL,8,Fnorthern Scotland, with increasing
OL,9,Fcloud and rain later. Light winds,
OL,10,Fcool northeast, warm south.
